[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

You really don't like partner's \Ss, and you do have 8 points. But 8 points is not enough to be considering game, and you would have to bid your \Hs at the 2-level. All things considered it is better to pass while you still aren't doubled.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
