[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.  

You overcall 2\H and hear partner raise you to 3\H.  

No matter how many times you check this hand you cannot revalue it any more than 13 points. Since partner has 10 at the most you reluctantly pass.}

